OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry today with a few
OL,6,Fbright or sunny spells at times.
OL,7,FHowever, cloud will thicken around the
OL,8,Fnorth coast bringing some showery
OL,9,Foutbreaks of rain occasionally.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FStaying cloudy overnight,
OL,12,Fperhaps with the odd spot of rain at
OL,13,Ftimes, but mostly dry for many. The
OL,14,Fblanket of cloud will hold
OL,15,Ftemperatures well above freezing.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FCloudy and grey to start
OL,18,Fthe day. Remaining cloudy in the west
OL,19,Fwith showers at times, but clouding
OL,20,Fthinning in the east to bring a few
OL,21,Fbrighter spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
