OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FLargely cloudy in the coming day with
OL,7,Fscattered showers at times. Some
OL,8,Fbrighter spells are possible too.
OL,9,FTurning warmer.
